{"tid":1697873,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一信救斬妖義士","createTime":"2019-11-07T06:17:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-07T06:30:20.000Z","uid":104309,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c2877a8be374b9474407bff5326024ca59c3709e","tid":1697873,"uid":104309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T06:17:15.000Z","msg":"斬妖義士的勇氣，本應受萬人景仰，昨日卻淪為鼠輩。至今日終於真相大白，本應受眾人關注。但眾人因為一時意氣，及後不敢自揭瘡疤，只道歉了事，不重視，不關注，以保面子。<br />\n<br />\n白話文版: <br />\n斬妖義士刺殺對象係何黑，義士依家任黑道魚肉，本來黑道斷人手腳係小菜一碟，再加上黑警相助，義士變死士亦唔難。<br />\n<br />\n我地做到嘅嘢好簡單，一人一信予各大媒體，密切留意義士去向，保護義士免受私刑之難。<br />\n<br />\n最後，香港人，你地無柒到，呢個唔係你地瘡疤，只係政府搞到大家咁多疑。推post 加email 救手足，保得一個得一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e99a350b2eed31bd0fc6833254169fd0644e3a6f","tid":1697873,"uid":104309,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T06:19:17.000Z","msg":"斬妖義士嘅去向，受到嘅對待，將係大眾目光所在，希望大家略盡綿力"},{"pid":"307901a27c96287e281d3346e107f2fe3fd596c7","tid":1697873,"uid":104309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T06:19:38.000Z","msg":"急推"},{"pid":"e633a03e279c13e2d3a4c395d7155336961f4c62","tid":1697873,"uid":104309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T06:20:00.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"3a02be405daba5ece438f835917f3b248b85e412","tid":1697873,"uid":104309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T06:21:14.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ec133f1e96352ddfb0940aaa0115631dfe3a2e75","tid":1697873,"uid":104309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T06:21:24.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6a39b5b9a15f5ff1cd3e8dd1fecb8fe3ee27814b","tid":1697873,"uid":104309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T06:25:53.000Z","msg":"救人！"},{"pid":"4a31cf55a2838c2c355c005e4d58c772920ec3ca","tid":1697873,"uid":104309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T06:26:45.000Z","msg":"快推"},{"pid":"d8b8e59bbcdd2f92ecafb39058550fadfd780b74